type: task_result
title: Local I2V vs fal.ai Comparison Test Results
key_insights[5]: "CogVideoX-5B on M4 Max MPS: 11+ minutes elapsed, 0/30 steps completed → completely impractical","fal.ai MiniMax Hailuo: 4.2 min, $0.28/clip, 3.5 MB output → production ready","Estimated local generation time: 5-7.5 hours per 5-second clip (extrapolated from step timing)","MPS backend for CogVideoX is ~100x slower than CUDA RTX 4090, making it useless for production",6 video scenes × $0.28 = $1.68 (~250円) total with fal.ai → highly cost effective
decisions[1]:
  - chose: fal.ai MiniMax Hailuo for all 6 video scenes
    over[2]: Local CogVideoX-5B (too slow),Hybrid approach (no benefit since local fails)
    reason: "Local CogVideoX-5B on M4 Max MPS is completely impractical (11+ min for 0/30 steps). fal.ai delivers in 4.2 min for $0.28/clip. Total cost for 6 clips: ~$1.68 (250円)."
